title: Bobby's Mailbag + Lunchbox Tries To Buy Johnny Cash's House + Riddle Me This
itunes:title: Bobby's Mailbag + Lunchbox Tries To Buy Johnny Cash's House + Riddle Me This
description:
Bobby opens the mailbag and helps a listener out with a question about an iPhone for a kid. Lunchbox calls a Nashville realtor and tries to make a bid on Johnny's Cash's Tennessee home. Plus, Bobby hosts another round of 'Riddle Me This' with show members trying to answer easy kids riddles!
